extracted_text: CELL (7, 2): Maximum Lot Coverage (% of lot area)

[6] The maximum lot coverage may be increased with approval from NCDEQ and compliance with all applicable stormwater management
requirements.
llm_outputs.rationale: The table in the Maritime Commercial (MC) District section specifies the maximum lot coverage for residential development as 24%. The footnote [6] indicates that this value may be increased with approval and compliance with stormwater management requirements. This aligns with our definition of max_lot_coverage as it refers to the percentage of lot area that can be covered by buildings.
